title: Brahms - The Cello Sonatas - Serkin, Rostropovich
description:
Brahms: The Cello Sonatas.

This is my own personal favourite version of these two gorgeous works; it features the peerless duo of Rudolf Serkin (piano) and Mstislav Rostropovich (cello). It was released by DG in 1983. (Funny to remember: in 1983 it was mainly purchased as a record or a cassette tape! I didn't know anyone with a CD player in 1983.)

Please enjoy.
